column5: From my OFC homies. Need some votes on a contest pic of my pooch. Would be much appreciated if y'all could throw a vote or two. https://contest.mypetsies.com/entries/182231631
I can't seem to be able to open the link. I select it and it brings me back to this thread?????
Looks like it already has a name?  	If not, Chief Crazy Eyes.

That's more better. Beauty pooch. The hat though? My former wife used to dress up my puppy and I didn't appreciate it. She got my dog in the settlement, not even visitation rights and she didn't like the dog!!!
Done. It seems you're allowed to vote every 25 minutes. It says I can vote again after the countdown timer. I wonder why they allow that? Good luck Dave.
How bad am I going to get spammed after giving them my email addy? LOL Votes In. Dan.
Give them a fake one, lol.
Gonna take a miracle to win this one. An ugly  half blind 3 legged cat has over 2000 votes.  ?
That won't work as you have to respond to an email to confirm your vote.

Did it a couple days ago, responded to confirm and waiting for spam.  Pleased to say none yet!  If it were gonna happen it woulda happened by now, so no happenin' is a good happenin'!  Shoot the cat Dave, y'alls dog is a much better candidate!  Michael
